components.name: Load Customer Segment CSV
components.description: Loads customer segmentation data from a CSV file into memory for downstream marketing campaigns.

connections.purpose: Read customer segment CSV file from local disk

components.name: Send Email Campaign
components.description: Sends email marketing messages to premium customers using the loaded segment data.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful loading of customer segment data

connections.purpose: Send email messages via the email delivery system

components.name: Send SMS Campaign
components.description: Sends SMS marketing messages with exclusive deals to customers using the loaded segment data.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful loading of customer segment data

connections.purpose: Send SMS messages via the SMS delivery gateway

components.name: Send Push Notification
components.description: Sends push notifications to mobile app users using the loaded segment data.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful loading of customer segment data

connections.purpose: Send push notifications via the mobile push notification service

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

sources: Customer segment CSV file containing columns: customer_id, segment, email, phone, device_token
sinks: Email campaign execution results stored via Email Delivery Service
SMS campaign execution results stored via SMS Gateway
Push notification campaign execution results stored via Push Notification Service
intermediate_datasets: loaded_customer_segment_data (inmemory representation of the CSV records)
